title: TINKR Taps Tyler Cameron & Tate Madden to Lead Next Growth Phase
description: Tyler Cameron, TINKR partner and Head of Product, and Tate Madden, TINKR partner and Head of Creative, discuss the company’s next growth phase and what’s ahead with Romaine Bostick and Katie Greifeld on “The Close.” They say TINKR puts a “pretty” twist on home improvement. (Source: Bloomberg)
